print(f"ğŸ“ˆ Performance Trend / æ€§èƒ½è¶‹åŠ¿: {batch_analysis['trend_analysis']['performance_trend']}")
print(f"âš ï¸ Common Issues / å¸¸è§é—®é¢˜: {batch_analysis['common_issues']}")
print(f"âœ¨ Best Practices / æœ€ä½³å®è·µ: {batch_analysis['best_practices']}")
```

### â±ï¸ Real-time Progress Tracking / å®æ—¶è¿›åº¦è·Ÿè¸ª
```python
